'''Carole Umulinga Karemera''' wavutse 1975 n'umukinnyi wa filimi umubyinnyi, umucuranzi w'inanga ya saxofone ndetse akaba n'umwanditsi. Karemera yashinze ikigo k'imyidagaduro ndetse akaba akibereye n'umuyobozi Ishyo Art Center.

== Amateka ==
Yavutse mu 1975 i Buruseli mu bubirigi, n'umukobwa w’abanyarwanda bari mu buhungiro.  Akiri umwana, Karemara yari umuhanga mu mibare kandi arota gufungura ubucuruzi bw'ihariye bwo gukora imigati.  Karemera yize muri National Conservatory of Theatre and Dance i Buruseli. ninaho yarangirije amashuri ye ya kaminuza mu 1994, ise,yari umunyamakuru, yasubiye mu Bubiligi biturutse kuri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Jenoside yo]] mu Rwanda. <ref name="LM2004" /> Karemera yavumbuye u Rwanda kuri moto mu 1996. <ref name="Libe2018" /> Yakinnye mu makinamico menshi, nka The Trojan Women by Euripides, Umugore w'umuzimu ya Kay Adshead, na Anathema, mbere yo gutangira umwuga we wa film. <ref name="newtimes" /> Hagati ya 2000 na 2004, yagize uruhare runini mu Rwanda muruganda rwa sinema.    

== Umukinnyi wa filime ==
Mu 2005, Karemara yakinnye nka Jeanne muri filime ya Raoul Peck ''Rimwe na rimwe muri Mata'', ivuga kuri jenoside yo mu Rwanda.  Muri uwo mwaka, yahisemo gutura i [[Kigali]] .  Amaze kwimukira mu gihugu, Karemara yagize uruhare mu mishinga y’umuco, harimo no gukina amakinamico mu tubari no mu mihanda yo mu mijyi y’u Rwanda, kugira ngo amateka rusange akomeze amenyekane kandi asigasirwe. Afatanije na Cécilia Kankonda, yashyizeho "katedrali yumvikana" yaririmbwe mu majwi yo kwibukwa aho abitabiriye amahugurwa bashoboraga kuvuga ibyo bibuka ku Rwanda mbere ya 1994.  

== Ishyo Art Center ==
Mu 2006, Karemara n'abandi bagore barindwi bashinze ikigo cy’ubuhanzi cya Ishyo i Kigali kugira ngo bashyigikire umuco mu murwa mukuru, utari ufite ikinamico kugeza icyo gihe. <ref>http://www.ishyoartscentre.org/121/</ref> Karemera niwe muyobozi mukuru wiki kigo gifite byinshi mu guteza imbere umuco harimo ibitabo, kwiga kuyina, gukina ikinamico ndetse nibindi.

Karemara yakinnye nka Beatrice muri film ya ''Juju Uruganda'' 2007. Yabonye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza muri Festival Sinema Africano mu Butaliyani.  Yanditse ikinamico "Chez l'habitant", ivuga ku byabaye ku bagore i Buruseli, Kigali na Sevran. 

Karemara yabaye umunyamabanga wungirije w’urusobe rwa Arterial, ndetse n’uhagarariye umuryango wa Arterial Network mu Rwanda.<ref>http://www.arterialnetwork.org/network/member/carole-karemera/</ref>  Yakinnye mu mukino wa ''Battlefield wa'' Peter Brook mu 2016<ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/mag/269360/culture/theatre-battlefield-une-femme-sur-un-champ-de-bataille/</ref>, ashingiye kuri ''Mahabharata'' .  Muri 2018, yahawe igihembo muri Les Journées théâtrales de Carthage, yishimira ibikorwa bye mu ikinamico mu Rwanda. 

